name: BoJo
0:
”Alexa open Bo Jo”
”Catch a creature”
”What creatures do I have?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bo jo
des: A game to catch all the creatures. Have BoJo catch you a creature including a Gobolo, Weltim, Eggshem, Hooteray, Lipersnap, and a Mitlew that is just a few you and BoJo can catch. Check on your Alexa app, Echo Show, or Echo dot to see the creature caught. New creatures are coming soon. Have BoJo read how many creatures you have and to release the duplicate creatures.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
